data.title: TRIBALISTAS 2 (2017) LP / POLYSOM (BRAZIL) 333391
data.meta_description:
3 of Brazils most important artists of the past 10 years team up in this Tribalistas project ¬ù a genre-blurring set of tracks that recalls similar efforts of the Tropicalista generation, updated to reflect the styles of the 3 artists involved, with some nice complicated production touches from Monte herself. Titles include Carnavalia, La De Longe, O Amor E Feio, Passe Em Casa, Velha Infancia, and Ja Sei Namorar.
